<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 14:08:14 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>据《华盛顿邮报》报道，以色列军队似乎正在利用加沙医院、学校作为基地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/israeli-army-appears-to-be-using-gaza-hospital-school-as-bases-washington-post-reports/0000018f-868c-d443-adef-9fcc60e20000</link><description>卫星图像显示 11 月在土耳其-巴勒斯坦友谊医院周围以及 3 月在 Juhor ad Dik 学校附近修建土堤。上个月，《国土报》发布了卫星图像，显示以色列国防军部队集中在附近的内扎里姆走廊沿线。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 13:43:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/israeli-army-appears-to-be-using-gaza-hospital-school-as-bases-washington-post-reports/0000018f-868c-d443-adef-9fcc60e20000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争是悲惨的，但没有发生种族灭绝：以色列在国际法庭上陈述案情</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/war-in-gaza-tragic-but-no-genocide-taking-place-israel-presents-its-case-at-world-court/0000018f-85ef-d7f9-a5ff-b5ff9a610000</link><description>以色列提出论点，要求国际法院驳回南非停止在拉法行动并从加沙地带撤军的请求。预计下周将就紧急措施请求做出决定</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 11:11:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/war-in-gaza-tragic-but-no-genocide-taking-place-israel-presents-its-case-at-world-court/0000018f-85ef-d7f9-a5ff-b5ff9a610000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在对他来说唯一重要的战争中占据上风：保持权力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-has-the-upper-hand-in-the-only-war-that-matters-to-him-staying-in-power/0000018f-82a7-d7f9-a5ff-b7f725d80000</link><description>任何声称以色列总理没有战略的人都是错误的：政治生存高于一切 ■ 一句话概括了以色列处理加沙战争的悲剧</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 03:00:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-has-the-upper-hand-in-the-only-war-that-matters-to-him-staying-in-power/0000018f-82a7-d7f9-a5ff-b7f725d80000</guid></item><item><title>美国大使：几个月来我们一直在说以色列需要为后哈马斯加沙制定计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/u-s-ambassador-weve-been-saying-for-months-israel-needs-a-plan-for-post-hamas-gaza/0000018f-8117-d430-a38f-c5f75aa70000</link><description>大使杰克·卢告诉《国土报》，以色列必须解决战后谁管理加沙的问题。他补充说，以色列在拉法的军事行动迄今为止尚未跨越美国总统乔·拜登划定的底线</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 03:00:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/u-s-ambassador-weve-been-saying-for-months-israel-needs-a-plan-for-post-hamas-gaza/0000018f-8117-d430-a38f-c5f75aa70000</guid></item><item><title>“真正的越南化”：内塔尼亚胡在加沙的战略僵局引发了越来越多的公众异议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-faces-war-on-every-front-but-netanyahu-and-his-arsonist-allies-fan-the-flames/0000018f-82fb-d430-a38f-c7ffc5770000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡在宣扬以色列在加沙地带进行军事统治的想法时，追随了本-格维尔和斯莫特里奇的极右路线。 ■ 在以色列国防军，军官们全神贯注于晋升和解雇问题</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 03:00:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-faces-war-on-every-front-but-netanyahu-and-his-arsonist-allies-fan-the-flames/0000018f-82fb-d430-a38f-c7ffc5770000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称，从黎巴嫩向以色列北部和戈兰高地发射了 75 枚火箭弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article-live/israelis-attack-troops-who-treated-palestinian-driver-whose-truck-was-torched-by-settlers/0000018f-8436-d7f9-a5ff-b57610bd0000</link><description>以色列要求国际法院驳回南非的停火请愿 ■ 黎巴嫩报道称，真主党高级指挥官在西顿附近的以色列袭击中丧生 ■ 法国警察击毙试图纵火犹太教堂的武装人员 ■ 美国军方称第一批卡车装载的货物大量援助物资穿过美国码头进入加沙 ■ 真主党声称对向西加利利发射战斗无人机负责 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部表示，自战争爆发以来，有 35,303 名加沙人在加沙地带丧生 ■ 以色列国防军士兵在加沙附近的意外爆炸中丧生</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 01:52:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article-live/israelis-attack-troops-who-treated-palestinian-driver-whose-truck-was-torched-by-settlers/0000018f-8436-d7f9-a5ff-b57610bd0000</guid></item><item><title>“我认识的每个人现在都在以色列。圣彼得堡已没有一个熟人了。</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-05-17/ty-article/.highlight/everyone-i-ever-knew-is-now-in-israel-not-one-acquaintance-remained-in-st-petersburg/0000018f-838c-d430-a38f-c7ecd07f0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一位对以色列有责任感的俄罗斯移民，以及分别在以色列、美国和荷兰之间生活的三个兄弟姐妹</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 23:35:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-05-17/ty-article/.highlight/everyone-i-ever-knew-is-now-in-israel-not-one-acquaintance-remained-in-st-petersburg/0000018f-838c-d430-a38f-c7ecd07f0000</guid></item><item><title>“在哈马斯的囚禁期间，我遇到了一些女孩，她们说：我们将无法应对我们所经历的一切”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-hamas-captivity-i-met-girls-who-said-we-wont-be-able-to-cope-with-what-we-endured/0000018f-830d-d9d6-a38f-87ffe88c0000</link><description>迄今为止，政府新闻办公室拍摄了被释放的以色列俘虏数小时的证词，最终形成了一段 14 分钟的类似公共服务的剪辑。但没有什么可以掩盖前人质所讲述的恐怖</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 22:35:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-hamas-captivity-i-met-girls-who-said-we-wont-be-able-to-cope-with-what-we-endured/0000018f-830d-d9d6-a38f-87ffe88c0000</guid></item><item><title>美国众议院通过有争议的法案，迫使拜登向以色列运送已暂停的炸弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/u-s-house-passes-contentious-bill-forcing-biden-to-deliver-paused-bomb-shipment-to-israel/0000018f-8315-d7f9-a5ff-b77790f90000</link><description>白宫已经表示，如果这项“极其不严肃”的法案提交总统办公桌，它将予以否决</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 21:14:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/u-s-house-passes-contentious-bill-forcing-biden-to-deliver-paused-bomb-shipment-to-israel/0000018f-8315-d7f9-a5ff-b77790f90000</guid></item><item><title>“为阻止阿拉伯接管而感到自豪”：以色列的斯莫特里奇证实《纽约时报》的调查，称其为“血腥诽谤”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/proud-to-prevent-arab-takeover-smotrich-confirms-nyt-investigation-dubs-it-blood-libel/0000018f-82c9-d430-a38f-c7ed60800000</link><description>斯莫特里奇在回应一份已发布的文件时写道：“我很自豪能够战斗并阻止阿拉伯人占领这些领土，并帮助定居西岸的犹太英雄合法化。该文件指责他破坏了取缔非法定居点建设的努力。”</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 20:23:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/proud-to-prevent-arab-takeover-smotrich-confirms-nyt-investigation-dubs-it-blood-libel/0000018f-82c9-d430-a38f-c7ed60800000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡政府告诉高等法院，计划推进甘茨的正统法案草案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-government-tells-high-court-it-plans-to-advance-gantzs-haredi-draft-bill/0000018f-82d2-d430-a38f-c7f619650000</link><description>以色列总检察长表示，议员本尼·甘茨提交并经上届政府一读批准的征兵法不适合该国目前的安全形势。尽管如此，政府部长们表示他们计划在七月底之前批准该法案</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 20:19:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-government-tells-high-court-it-plans-to-advance-gantzs-haredi-draft-bill/0000018f-82d2-d430-a38f-c7f619650000</guid></item><item><title>加拿大因约旦河西岸暴力事件对四名以色列人实施制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/canada-sanctions-four-israelis-over-west-bank-violence/0000018f-82ed-d720-a79f-abff122f0000</link><description>加拿大效仿美国和英国采取的类似措施，针对被控对巴勒斯坦人及其财产实施暴力的四名个人，并禁止他们进入加拿大</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 20:13:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/canada-sanctions-four-israelis-over-west-bank-violence/0000018f-82ed-d720-a79f-abff122f0000</guid></item><item><title>即使给以色列带来灾难，内塔尼亚胡和他的伙伴也不会停止</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-his-partners-will-not-stop-even-after-bringing-disaster-upon-israel/0000018f-82a5-d430-a38f-c7e51d600000</link><description>战争的延长、总理在国内外的软弱以及以色列正在成为贱民国家的事实只会加剧内塔尼亚胡的救世主情结</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 19:36:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-his-partners-will-not-stop-even-after-bringing-disaster-upon-israel/0000018f-82a5-d430-a38f-c7e51d600000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方称，两名泰国人质于 10 月 7 日被杀，他们的尸体被哈马斯扣押在加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-says-two-thai-hostages-were-killed-on-oct-7-their-bodies-held-in-gaza-by-hamas/0000018f-82cb-d720-a79f-abdb31e70000</link><description>两名泰国公民 Sonthaya Oakkharasri 和 Sudthisak Rinthalak 在 Be&amp;#39;eri 基布兹附近的种植园工作，被哈马斯恐怖分子枪杀。军方称哈马斯在加沙扣押的132名人质中有40人被杀</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 19:28:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-says-two-thai-hostages-were-killed-on-oct-7-their-bodies-held-in-gaza-by-hamas/0000018f-82cb-d720-a79f-abdb31e70000</guid></item><item><title>“自 1967 年以来，以色列从未赢得过任何战争”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ever-since-1967-israel-hasnt-managed-to-win-any-war/0000018f-81ec-d9d6-a38f-85ffd5910000</link><description>双桅船。多夫·塔马里将军（退役）表示，以色列国防机构负责人应该告诉内塔尼亚胡总理，他无权管理加沙战争。在一次采访中，他谈到了秘密突击队核行动，并声称你无法在军事上击败恐怖组织</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 19:16:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ever-since-1967-israel-hasnt-managed-to-win-any-war/0000018f-81ec-d9d6-a38f-85ffd5910000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军命名在加沙边境附近武器意外爆炸中丧生的士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-soldier-killed-in-accidental-weaponry-explosion-near-gaza-border/0000018f-82b3-d720-a79f-abf3cb1f0000</link><description>中士。兰·亚维茨 (Ran Yavetz) 少校是一天内因行动事故而丧生的第六名以色列士兵，此前，加沙北部有五名士兵因以色列坦克意外开火而丧生</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 19:08:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-soldier-killed-in-accidental-weaponry-explosion-near-gaza-border/0000018f-82b3-d720-a79f-abf3cb1f0000</guid></item><item><title>由于担心藐视法庭，以色列教育部允许以色列-巴勒斯坦丧亲家庭团体返回学校</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/education-ministry-allows-israeli-palestinian-bereaved-families-group-to-return-to-schools/0000018f-8276-d430-a38f-c7f66ec60000</link><description>上个月，耶路撒冷地方法院命令以色列政府允许“家长圈-家庭论坛”继续举行学生与以色列和巴勒斯坦死者家属之间的会议，但教育部直到现在才这样做</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 18:52:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/education-ministry-allows-israeli-palestinian-bereaved-families-group-to-return-to-schools/0000018f-8276-d430-a38f-c7f66ec60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列真正的问题是内塔尼亚胡和他的极右翼盟友更喜欢哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-16/ty-article/.highlight/israels-real-problem-is-that-netanyahu-and-his-far-right-allies-prefer-hamas/0000018f-827e-d7f9-a5ff-b77eb8aa0000</link><description>如果内塔尼亚胡如愿以偿，而国防部长加兰特的警告被忽视，哈马斯将再次成为加沙的统治者——为内塔尼亚胡提供他对以色列下次选举的主要承诺：消灭该组织</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 18:17:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-16/ty-article/.highlight/israels-real-problem-is-that-netanyahu-and-his-far-right-allies-prefer-hamas/0000018f-827e-d7f9-a5ff-b77eb8aa0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列国防部长刚刚对内塔尼亚胡的加沙战争瘫痪打破沉默</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/why-israels-defense-minister-just-broke-his-silence-about-netanyahus-gaza-war-paralysis/0000018f-81fb-d720-a79f-abfbebf10000</link><description>以色列国防部长加兰特在新闻发布会上呼吁在加沙制定“事后计划”，这是他第三次公开批评内塔尼亚胡。虽然它不会让内塔尼亚胡垮台，但预示着更多的动荡</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 17:33:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/why-israels-defense-minister-just-broke-his-silence-about-netanyahus-gaza-war-paralysis/0000018f-81fb-d720-a79f-abfbebf10000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列心理健康危机的加剧，儿童和青少年精神科医生纷纷离开公共部门</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/as-mental-health-crisis-in-israel-grows-child-psychiatrists-leave-public-sector-in-droves/0000018f-81df-d720-a79f-abdf54270000</link><description>议会健康委员会提供的数据显示，尽管自 10 月 7 日以来儿童和青少年的心理健康问题有所增加，但需要心理健康专业人员的青少年可能需要等待八个月或更长时间才能得到治疗</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 17:17:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/as-mental-health-crisis-in-israel-grows-child-psychiatrists-leave-public-sector-in-droves/0000018f-81df-d720-a79f-abdf54270000</guid></item></channel></rss>